      "id": "PopularPost18087",
      "post_content": "Top 10 **Enchantment-Aura** (enchant creature) cards:\n  \n1. [Rancor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rancor) 2. [Pacifism](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pacifism) 3. [Treachery](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Treachery) 4. [Blanchwood Armor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blanchwood Armor) 5.[Armadillo Cloak](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Armadillo Cloak) 6. [Faith's Fetters](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Faith's Fetters) 7. [Spirit Link](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spirit Link) 8. [Control Magic](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Control Magic) 9. [Pillory of the Sleepless](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pillory of the Sleepless) 10. [Soul Link](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Soul Link)   \nThese are in no particular order. Also, they have garnered at least 4 star ratings.",
      "posted_by": "liir007",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost18087\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">Top 10 <b>Enchantment-Aura</b> (enchant creature) cards:\r<br/>1. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rancor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rancor\">Rancor</a> 2. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pacifism\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pacifism\">Pacifism</a> 3. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Treachery\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Treachery\">Treachery</a> 4. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blanchwood Armor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blanchwood Armor\">Blanchwood Armor</a> 5.<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Armadillo Cloak\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Armadillo Cloak\">Armadillo Cloak</a> 6. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Faith's Fetters\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Faith's Fetters\">Faith's Fetters</a> 7. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spirit Link\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spirit Link\">Spirit Link</a> 8. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Control Magic\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Control Magic\">Control Magic</a> 9. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pillory of the Sleepless\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pillory of the Sleepless\">Pillory of the Sleepless</a> 10. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Soul Link\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Soul Link\">Soul Link</a> <br/>These are in no particular order. Also, they have garnered at least 4 star ratings.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '18087'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2698\">liir007</span>\r\n                                (8/14/2009 7:09:50 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
