    {
      "id": "PopularPost295079",
      "post_content": "All these comments about putting this on an opponent's creature, and nobody, not even TheWrathOfShane, mentions that you do this *in order to get attackers through.*  \n  \n\"I swing with my 3/2 and my 1/2. Care to block with that 6/6?\"  \n  \n// \"yeah, mayb--\"  \n  \n\"Remember, if you do, I'll gain six life off Spirit Link.\"  \n  \n// \"....\\*sigh\\* ok, I'll take the 4.\"  \n  \nIt's more interesting than Pacifism because it plays headgames with your opponent. Pacify their 5/5 and they treat it as gone, and play accordingly. Spirit Link their 5/5 and they agonize over every combat decision--their neutralized creature actually becomes *more* present in their mind, rather than less, resulting in more bad decisions or play mistakes.  \n  \nAlso, [Alpha Brawl](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Alpha Brawl). For the lulz.",
      "posted_by": "Salient",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost295079\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">All these comments about putting this on an opponent's creature, and nobody, not even TheWrathOfShane, mentions that you do this <i>in order to get attackers through.</i><br/><br/>\"I swing with my 3/2 and my 1/2. Care to block with that 6/6?\"<br/><br/>// \"yeah, mayb--\"<br/><br/>\"Remember, if you do, I'll gain six life off Spirit Link.\"<br/><br/>// \"....*sigh* ok, I'll take the 4.\"<br/><br/>It's more interesting than Pacifism because it plays headgames with your opponent. Pacify their 5/5 and they treat it as gone, and play accordingly. Spirit Link their 5/5 and they agonize over every combat decision--their neutralized creature actually becomes <i>more</i> present in their mind, rather than less, resulting in more bad decisions or play mistakes.<br/><br/>Also, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Alpha Brawl\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Alpha Brawl\">Alpha Brawl</a>. For the lulz.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '295079'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy67559\">Salient</span>\r\n                                (1/27/2013 12:10:32 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating