      "id": "PopularPost21898",
      "post_content": "this and [vamperic Link](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=vamperic Link) on any creature with a [pyroclasm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=pyroclasm) ability results in massive life gain. Cards like [Oros, the Avenger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oros, the Avenger), [Infected Vermin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Infected Vermin), and [Skirk Fire Marshal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skirk Fire Marshal) make the most out of this because they take small increments of damage, and turn it into a massive gain.",
      "posted_by": "darkfury",
